Movie production. 2009. Since the start of my acting career, no matter what I did or who I worked with, I appreciated every opportunity I received. The film industry is small, and you never know when you might run into people you've offended or shown disrespect to. Acting isn't for everyone. Even if you work hard and have the best coach, you may not get a job. You need to be emotionally strong and ready for that. It's important to respect and find joy in every project, even if it's not your dream one. That's where it all begins. I am so grateful for every single person who believed on my on every step of my career💫
#mood

Today is my birthday, and I’ve chosen to let go of the past that held me back. I’ve released a song about it in my native language. This is the last song in Russian, I’m moving forward to another step of my music career and this is about saying goodbye to the past version of myself! Thanks for your birthday wishes and support! Hope you’re going to enjoy it!🥳😇
The world premiere will be on July 18th at 12:00am Eastern Time on YouTube.
Check it out!

🍁 Happy Thanksgiving, everyone! 🍂

Today is a beautiful reminder of how blessed and grateful I am. Life's journey is full of twists, but I always strive to find the silver lining in every cloud✨

Grateful for every person who has stepped into my life – whether they stayed or moved on

Each encounter shapes my path. Thankful for the opportunities I seized and those I missed, and even for those who said no. Your leaving made room for something truly meant for me🙌

Big shoutout to family and friends – your support during tough times means the world🤗

And a special thanks to myself for not giving up🌟 
Maybe one day, I'll share my story here, or maybe not. But for now, I trust that everything happening is for a reason.

Happy Thanksgiving, and may your hearts be full with joy and happiness 🦃💕 #gratitude#thanksgivingvibe #blessedandgrateful#happythanksgivng
